title: calculations
text: The number of calculations does not give insight into whether the query is valid.

title: fields
text: Knowing the number of fields will not help in validating the query since the query is changing the data and not the fields.

title: records
text: If the number of records is reasonable for the query, then it means it is valid.

title: data types
text: Knowing the different amounts of data type will not help with validating whether the query was correct because the data might have changed.
